What does it mean in golf to “play from the tips”
aw i love golf questions from you

you know how at golf courses, for each of the 18 holes, there are mens tee boxes and women’s tee boxes from where golfers start each of the 18 holes from? these are designated areas. women’s tee boxes are closer to the hole you’re trying to get it. one tee box and one hole for each of the 18 different holes on the course. If man, you play the men’s tees from each hole, drive up, and then the women tee off. however, for men, there are normal tee boxes that are right behind the women’s tee boxes, but then the difficulty goes up as courses put additional tee boxes even behind the men’s tee boxes. typically 2. The furthest tee box from the hole is the tip. so the tips are playing from the hardest, furthest tee box from all 18 holes

In a moment of habit, I took a picture to share. Then, this sadness is so strong. To not send it means so much. It's our family. It's our Lu. We raised her together and we have grown with her, shes seen us every day loving each other, always seemingly nudging her self into a space we make room for - that little head getting between our knees to just get a piece of every loving moment. I cant bring myself to not send it but i took this picture hours ago. Before it, i took 5 others i couldnt bring myself to share and then the guilt that came from deleting a small gift - one sharing a moment while youre at work, the family that is so accustomer to that amazing of you coming home from work. 

I've read and reread your two texts all day, drafted a half dozen responses, deleting every lucy picture you always appreciate so much, 

I'm in a space of only lost sadness. I have no fight in me to contend with you. I reiterated to you my unconditional love to last night. No conditions, only love and any support or effort you need of me, i wanted you to know its okay and im always going to love you more every day. So you have it. If these are your conditions, terms are your setting to challenge my unconditional promise, then you have it, you have whatever resource we have together, without terms, without resistance, without conditions.

I replay yesterday over and over. This cloud over has existed for so long- we acknowlegde it's there. We talk about it. But when we agree in the foundation of love that survives despite, we nod to its existence because we have always overcome our own selves, and any circumstance, any imperfection. You understand that cloud so intimately, far better than i do. I want so badly to face it with you.

The level of pain i see in your eyes, how it surfaces, how it speaks, it makes me lose any care for myself. I have no guard to fake. Im broken. Im losing you. 

I replay the last few days, yesterday’s birthday, and yesterdays conversation at the bayou over and over.

I think about how foolish I am or how dissapointing i have become to you. I keep kidding myself, falling for the existence of a love I swear exists, because it exists so strongly in me, for you, at a mutual level of love that gets challenged in every way but has only gotten stronger, making us stronger, our little family stronger. We kept proving ourselves right, and love always conquered on our behalf. 

For me, despite my imperfections, your imperfections, I felt so thankful to be loved by you regardless and to reciprocate the same…to get, and to give, those small moments that are so important, that represent what carries us through anything… love we both nod to and acknowledge, in agreement, it exists…unconditional love. I know what that is, and I know how beautiful it is. And i know how fleeting it had become in you, for me.
 
I carry no blame or resentment for this. Ive let go. I am deeply sad that I cannot understand your feelings. I am here to hear the harshest of opinions of me, my wrongdoings, and who you see ad your husband in these life struggles. 

I am the central point of months of my loved ones' attentions, and I see it unraveling as I'm approached from each corner within the smallest of family circles - unraveling all at the expense of me. Im done. Im only going to give moving forward. Love, money, help, conversations, if you want any of those and more, take it.

Please consider coming to therapy tomorrow at 4:45 pm with me. I will respect your request to leave you alone before and after, but please sleep on it. You dont have to talk in the session, only listen

I was kindly asked that you be left alone. So, as difficult as that is, im honoring that. I won't be coming home tonight. Or any time in the future.

Your desire to find your own place and for our money to fund two places isn't necessary if i leave. Its no longer a burden. You dont have to endure that of moving out, moving in somewhere else, then only to quickly move again back to Philly  

You are focused now on just you. I wanted that. Im accepting it and getting in your way is all i am doing simply be being, and existing in the same home as you. 

Since im not in your current equation or focus, there is no room in that equation for you, or i needing to know each others  location. Those alerts, coming and going and having that visibility doesnt align with your ask of me. So i removed my location permission from the life360 app. Please do the same.

You have no more responsibilities to burden you. I am not kidnapping Lucy. I want that to be known. Lucy is part of the “us” equation. It cant be part of the on focusing on you equation.

Im focusing on us, that includes me, but also includes you, and that included us, all three of us. In my mind, every day in the past and every day moving forward will be consumed with that focus, and to allow you the space you kindly asked me to provide you. 

The lease is paid in full now. You have that house until August 31st to use as you please. It's yours. I won't be coming back. Everything there is yours to keep, sell, or take with you. I only took what i needed to live and what lucy needed to live. Lucy is ours. She's focused on us forever. “Us” is one person to her. For me, “us” is collectively the three of us 
me + you + lucy. Thats the equation im focused on. With only love. 

If you need to talk to me for whatever reason im going to make myself available. If you cant reach me, say my phone is off or not next to me, there only a few places ill be in that moment. So you know where to find me, you know how to reach me, you know what im doing, and you have a good idea of where i am. Im available to you, just speak up. Until then, im going to hold my word. You have the space and i hopefully less a burden with me, without us, and a place to rest and plan whats next, whats best, for you. 

I texted barb. I want you to know that before i speak to her. Shes your sister and shes a great one to have. Im going to tell her what i see and feel. My concerns for you. Thank you for offering me the your blessing in doing that. I will not be calling Sherry, your dad, mary, or anyone else. I will hand over my love for you to barb as i trust her completely. You may join me at 4:45 at Marks to listen only if you want to. Im not requiring any commitment from you, especially one day later after you asked for space and shared the news that you wanted to not live in the same home as me, as us, and to do so for you. I will not leave out what my role is in this to barb, i will not present myself to be a victim. I am responsible for my role in this. But i can no longer support what you need. I have check. It was dated for yesterday but if you cash it, it will bounce. Ive sold pretty much every last investment to prepare it in an account that will be visible and available to you. Venmo has a cap in terms of how much i can send at once. If you need any amount immediately, i will venmo you as much as i can today. Our money is your money. And the jeep is yours to keep indefinitely. Whether you drive it home to philly, or leave it wherever, you can consider it yours.
